message.body: My peanut butter was the perfect consistency this morning; I feel accomplished
All that effort on saturday and putting it in the fridge did the trick
What are you doing next week? I know it's a bit in advance

Oh nothing out of the ordinary. I'd like to see you though.
I hope that that doesn't make me nothing out of the ordinary :-p but let's hang out!
Of course not. I've only known you a week
